cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

This paper deals with image retrieval, specifically in the context of foliage plant images. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). However, since the paper also discusses distance measures and their performance, it could also be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
